<TEXTAREA NAME="ReplyMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">[QUOTE]Originally posted by Aladain:
[B] The nerf your talking about it probably Donals BP being changed first from a 20 second cast time to a 30 second cast time, then a 30 second cast time only useable on one person once for every 7.5 minutes.

The reason I feel (and many others did) that this was unjustified was because Verant admited they designed mobs around this BP, and nerfed the BP because "No one item should cause us to create a mob a certain way".  The problem is they then buffed the very mobs they said the BP was designed after.  The only reason I think these mobs have been taken down is instead of bringing in 10 clerics, they are bringing in 20 clerics and also binding all clerics right next to the mob area so if they go oom they die so they will have mana to heal again.  Very goofy, not a real strategy, and more of a zergling rush approach, but nonetheless, the only approach.

Aladain
[/B][/QUOTE]

